jacdac.HumidityReg.Humidity:
Read-only %RH u22.10 (uint32_t). The relative humidity in percentage of full water saturation.
* ```
const [humidity] = jdunpack<[number]>(buf, "u22.10")
```
jacdac.HumidityReg.HumidityError:
Read-only %RH u22.10 (uint32_t). The real humidity is between `humidity - humidity_error` and `humidity + humidity_error`.
* ```
const [humidityError] = jdunpack<[number]>(buf, "u22.10")
```
jacdac.HumidityReg.MaxHumidity:
Constant %RH u22.10 (uint32_t). Highest humidity that can be reported.
* ```
const [maxHumidity] = jdunpack<[number]>(buf, "u22.10")
```
jacdac.HumidityReg.MinHumidity:
Constant %RH u22.10 (uint32_t). Lowest humidity that can be reported.
* ```
const [minHumidity] = jdunpack<[number]>(buf, "u22.10")
```
modules.HumidityClient: A sensor measuring humidity of outside environment.
modules.HumidityClient.humidity: The relative humidity in percentage of full water saturation.
modules.HumidityClient.humidityError: The real humidity is between `humidity - humidity_error` and `humidity + humidity_error`.
modules.HumidityClient.maxHumidity: Highest humidity that can be reported.
modules.HumidityClient.minHumidity: Lowest humidity that can be reported.
modules.HumidityClient.onHumidityChanged: Run code when the humidity changes by the given threshold value.
